      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 is a masterclass in analog engineering, featuring the high-revving F22C1 inline-four paired with a razor-sharp 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains factory-spec with all original VIN tags present, showcasing its preservation. Performance is anchored by a Torsen limited-slip differential and a double-wishbone suspension setup that provides surgical turn-in and exceptional mechanical grip. The naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque across the rev range, while the synchros remain crisp, offering that legendary bolt-action shift feel. Meticulously maintained with zero modifications, this is an investment-grade example for the discerning purist.",
